ISLAMABAD, Mar 29 (APP): The Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) on Wednesday notified that the general elections in the provincial assembly Khyber Pakhtunkhwa would be held on October 8, 2023.
According to ECP, the date of the poll has been conveyed by Khyber Pakhtunkhwaâ€™s Governor Ghulam Ali in compliance with orders of the Supreme Court of Pakistan in Suo Moto case no 1 of 2023, Constitutional Petition no 1&2 of 2023.
